public class GenericTableCellRenderer<T>
extends javax.swing.table.DefaultTableCellRenderer
implements Formattable<T>

TableCellRenderer that passes the contents through a functor to render the contents, instead of calling toString() on the contents. It is up to the user to ensure that the contents of the table are of the correct type, otherwise, a ClassCastException will be thrown during the compo
